The paper discusses a modulation scheme for communication systems, which falls under the field of information theory (cs.IT) and communication (cs.COMM). The study also considers the optimization of mutual information, which is a common metric in information theory and signal processing. The paper also mentions resource-limited links, which could fall under the sub-categories of sensor networks (cs.SI), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), and multimedia (cs.MM).
